        </div>
        <div class="turn assistant">
            <div class="turn-label">Assistant</div>
            <div>
                <div class="bubble"><p>Here’s a comparison table summarizing the customer journey for upgrading a home internet plan via a mobile app, including the stages, user actions, touchpoints, and emotional goals:</p>
