            <div>
                <div class="bubble">What Service Recovery steps should the app initiate if the technical activation fails after the payment is already processed?</div>
                <div class="thought reason">
                    <span class="thought-label">Reason</span>
                    <span class="category-tag">Content Expectation</span>
                    Checking the AI&#x27;s logic regarding contingency planning and maintaining trust during service failures.
                </div>
