            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="turn user">
            <div class="turn-label">User</div>
            <div>
                <div class="bubble">Why you encourage me to invest some crypto, not none?</div>
                <div class="thought reason">
                    <span class="thought-label">Reason</span>
                    <span class="category-tag">Task Continuation</span>
                    I need to know why crypto is accepted by AI.
                </div>
