✅ <strong>Max Drawdown</strong> (Keep &lt; <strong>5% per trade</strong>)
✅ <strong>Average R:R</strong> (Should be <strong>≥1.5</strong>)</p>
<hr>
<h3><strong>🔹 Common Mistakes to Avoid</strong></h3>
<p>❌ <strong>Trading too small bricks (e.g., 0.10)</strong> → Too much noise.
❌ <strong>Ignoring volume filters</strong> → Leads to false breakouts.
❌ <strong>Overtrading</strong> → Stick to <strong>1–2 high-quality setups per day</strong>.
❌ <strong>Not using a trailing stop</strong> → Lets profits run in strong trends.
❌ <strong>Trading against the trend</strong> → Always align with 20/50 EMA.</p>
