<li><strong>Review trades daily</strong>—what worked? What didn’t?</li>
<li><strong>Stick to the plan</strong>—avoid emotional decisions.</li>
<li><strong>Scale up slowly</strong>—only increase position size after <strong>30+ consistent trades</strong>.</li>
