<th>Details</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong>Renko Signal</strong></td>
<td><strong>Red brick closes below previous red brick’s low.</strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Volume Filter</strong></td>
<td><strong>Volume &gt; 20-day average</strong>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Trend Filter</strong></td>
<td><strong>20 EMA &lt; 50 EMA</strong> (bearish trend).</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Key Level</strong></td>
<td>Trade <strong>only if price is below recent swing low</strong>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Momentum</strong></td>
<td><strong>RSI(14) &lt; 50</strong> (avoid oversold).</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
