<h3><strong>Presentation Tips</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>Poster: Hypothesis → Methods → Data table/graph → Conclusion (e.g., "Voltage doubled removal rate by 1.5x").</li>
<li>Extension: Test pH changes or coatings (prevents re-rust?).</li>
</ul>
<p>Total time: 1 day trials + 1 day analysis. Under $10, impressive for science fair. Need diagrams, shopping list tweaks, or data spreadsheet help? Let me know! Good luck—you&#x27;ll crush it! 🚀</p></div>
