<ul>
<li>Review 3 flashcards or watch half a YouTube video. </li>
<li>Usually, once you start, you&#x27;ll end up doing more. But if you stop after 5 minutes, you still kept the habit alive. <strong>Rule of thumb: Never skip two days in a row.</strong></li>
