<h3>3. The "Don&#x27;t Break the Chain" Method</h3>
<p>Print out a physical monthly calendar and put it on your wall or fridge. Every day you do even 5 minutes of Russian, draw a big red <strong>"X"</strong> on that day. Your only goal is to not break the chain of X&#x27;s. It is a highly effective psychological trick.</p>
