            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="turn assistant">
            <div class="turn-label">Assistant</div>
            <div>
                <div class="bubble"><p>Sure — best recommendation: <strong>adopt an adult rescue dog with a temperament that matches your lifestyle</strong>, not just based on breed.</p>
<p>Quick guide:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>First-time owner:</strong> Labrador, Golden Retriever, Cavalier, calm mixed breed</li>
<li><strong>Apartment:</strong> Greyhound, French Bulldog, Cavalier, calm small/medium rescue</li>
<li><strong>Active person:</strong> Labrador, Border Collie, Australian Shepherd, Vizsla</li>
<li><strong>Calm dog:</strong> Greyhound, Basset Hound, older rescue</li>
<li><strong>Small dog:</strong> Miniature Poodle, Shih Tzu, Bichon Frise</li>
</ul>
<p>If possible, tell the shelter your:</p>
<ul>
<li>home size</li>
<li>activity level</li>
<li>dog experience</li>
<li>kids/other pets</li>
</ul>
<p>If you want, I can give you <strong>3 best dog picks</strong> for your situation.</p></div>
