        <div class="turn assistant">
            <div class="turn-label">Assistant</div>
            <div>
                <div class="bubble"><p><strong>Australian Shepherds</strong> are great dogs, but they&#x27;re <strong>not for everyone</strong>.</p>
<h3>Pros</h3>
<ul>
<li>Very smart and easy to train</li>
<li>Energetic and fun</li>
<li>Loyal and affectionate</li>
<li>Great if you like outdoor activities</li>
</ul>
<h3>Cons</h3>
<ul>
<li>Need <strong>a lot</strong> of exercise and mental stimulation</li>
