                <div class="bubble">Conde Duque sounds perfect for a quick break, ofc! Moving on to some gear—since I&#x27;m spending so much time in cafes, I&#x27;ve realized I really need a better laptop stand or even just a high-quality notebook for sketching out business models. Are there any cool independent stationery shops or small tech boutiques in Malasaña that sell unique items? I&#x27;d rather support a local shop than go to a giant department store like El Corte Inglés.</div>
