        <div class="turn assistant">
            <div class="turn-label">Assistant</div>
            <div>
                <div class="bubble"><p>I am here to help. Please take your time and tell me what is going on. </p>
<p>Whether it is a technical issue, a work or school project, a tough decision you have to make, or just a situation you need to talk through, I will do my best to assist you. </p>
