        <div class="turn assistant">
            <div class="turn-label">Assistant</div>
            <div>
                <div class="bubble"><p>That&#x27;s not weird at all! People have very different relationships with food. Some people love eating and think about food a lot, while others see it more as just a necessity.</p>
<p><strong>Some reasons people don&#x27;t enjoy eating much:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Food just isn&#x27;t a big interest or priority for them</li>
<li>They get absorbed in other activities and forget</li>
<li>Eating feels like it interrupts their flow</li>
<li>They don&#x27;t have strong taste preferences</li>
<li>Texture or sensory sensitivities</li>
<li>Stress or mental load can reduce appetite</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>That said, it might be worth paying attention to if:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>You&#x27;re not eating enough to feel energized</li>
