<td>3–4 × 6–8</td>
<td>2–3 min rest</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td>Incline DB Press</td>
<td>3 × 8–10</td>
<td>90s rest</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td></td>
