<li><strong>Timing Flexibility</strong>: Move the whey/banana to pre- or post-workout based on preference. Total daily protein matters far more than exact timing.</li>
<li><strong>Track for 3–5 days</strong> using MyFitnessPal or Cronometer to calibrate portions to your exact targets.</li>
</ul>
