<p><strong>Get a new lid</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Only if your current lid is:</li>
<li>Damaged or cracked</li>
<li>Doesn&#x27;t fit well with the bidet seat</li>
<li>You want a matched set aesthetically</li>
</ul>
<h2>Things to Check</h2>
<ul>
<li>Does your old lid still close properly?</li>
<li>Does it fit without hitting the Tushy controls/arm?</li>
<li>Is there any damage?</li>
</ul>
<p>If it works fine, save the money and keep it.</p>
