        </div>
        <div class="turn user">
            <div class="turn-label">User</div>
            <div>
                <div class="bubble">Do you think those cheaper presses like Vevor will hold up if I’m using them regularly, or is it worth spending more upfront? Any options you could find in Brazil?</div>
                <div class="thought reason">
                    <span class="thought-label">Reason</span>
